If a ".desktop" file is added or updated, launch the following command to
update the application database:

cd gnome/applications ; umask 002 ; update-desktop-database .

More information at https://help.gnome.org/admin/system-admin-guide/stable/mime-types-custom-user.html.en

To override the default registered application, create a file "mimeapps.list"
in this folder and follow the instructions at https://help.gnome.org/admin/system-admin-guide/stable/mime-types-application-user.html.en
